div.p:


            The Lord bleſſe your Maieſtie with all his bleſſings both ſpirituall and temporall, and who hath giuen you this particular bleſsing, that your Maieſtie may truely ſay with King Dauid;

Thou haſt deliuered me from the contentions of my people, Thou haſt preſerued mee to be the head ouer nations, the people which I knew not doe ſerue mee.

            And the Lord further grant that you and your Royall iſſue may gouerne vs and our poſterity in peace and happineſſe vnto the worlds end.
